title: Or not so much
author: VD
content_html: My apologies to Pretty Lady and Rainman, but the promised posts will have to wait at least a day, as I was bushwhacked by a bit of a cold that seems to have clogged up my synapses as well as the sinuses. I’m just going to lay around reading Jonathan Strange and Mr. Norrell, a Nebula-nominated novel by Susanna Clarke that is really very good indeed.
